OL,3,CPrince William praises 'incredible
OL,4,Cmilestone' as Bowelbabe Fund hits #20
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FThe Prince of Wales has praised the
OL,8,F"amazing legacy" of Dame Deborah James
OL,9,Fafter her Bowelbabe Fund passed the
OL,10,F#20 million milestone.
OL,12,FWilliam, in a personal message, wrote
OL,13,Fon Instagram: "What an incredible
OL,14,Fmilestone and an amazing legacy.
OL,16,F"Deborah is in our thoughts today, as
OL,17,Fare all those who loved her. W."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@PO]uD@OOUxD@AOUyD@`O]
