OL,3,CPrince William praises 'incredible
OL,4,Cmilestone' as Bowelbabe Fund hits #20
OL,5,Cmillion
OL,7,FThe Bowelbabe Fund for Cancer Research
OL,8,FUK supports cuttingedge research and
OL,9,Fraises awareness of bowel cancer. It
OL,10,Fwas launched in May 2022 with an
OL,11,Finitial target of #250,000.
OL,13,FYou, Me And The Big C podcast host
OL,14,FDame Deborah was given a damehood for
OL,15,Fher fundraising efforts, which soared
OL,16,Finto the millions.
OL,18,FThe honour was personally conferred by
OL,19,FWilliam, who joined her family for
OL,20,Fafternoon tea and champagne while she
OL,21,Fwas receiving hospice-at-home care.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/4
